Hard Assertions terminate from code when they failed.

Soft Asserions ignores failure and execute remaining code and final result failure only. 

Use soft Asserions for independent checks because it can find all errors at once not for everything.Hard Asserions will be usefulto check main fields.

Hard Asserion:
await expect(locator).toBe(value);

Soft Asserion:
await expect.soft(locator).toBe(value);